They will work on type4 engine tin, but they are a
bear to get seated.
On cyls #1 and #3, the plug boot is not long enough
(by about 1/8"") to extend up through the hole in the
tin, but if you are determined, you can get the seals
to seat.

Bug pack sells the exact same part.

